lass=\"c-newslist__date\">2025年12月1日</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__genre\"><div class=\"c-newslist__genre-name\">その他</div></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__title\">当社の社員が「国土交通省不動産・建設経済局長賞」を受賞しました。</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"c-newslist__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"c-newslist__link\" href=\"https://www.united-k.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/077d34424a3d7e494c63ef0db701620c.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__date\">2025年11月17日</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__genre\"><div class=\"c-newslist__genre-name\">企業情報</div></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__title\">当社の健康経営宣言について</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"p-f-biz\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"p-f-biz__inner\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-biz__head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"p-f-section-head__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-en\">Business</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-jp\">事業案内</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head__desc\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>解体現場などから出る産業廃棄物を燃焼し、その際に発生する熱エネルギーも無駄なく活用。環境負荷を抑えつつ、資源の循環と次世代エネルギーへの取り組みを通じて、持続可能な事業成長を目指しています。</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head__more\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"p-f-section-head__link\" href=\"/business/\">詳しく見る</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"p-f-biz__body\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-biz__image js-motion\"><span></span></div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-biz__loop\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-biz__loop-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"c-biz-loop\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"c-biz-loop__item\"><div class=\"c-biz-loop__circle\"><a class=\"c-biz-loop__link\" href=\"business/industrial-waste/\"><span>産業廃棄物<br>処理・処分</span></a></div></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"c-biz-loop__item\"><div class=\"c-biz-loop__circle\"><a class=\"c-biz-loop__link\" href=\"business/construction-and-demolition/\"><span>建設・解体</span></a></div></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"c-biz-loop__item\"><div class=\"c-biz-loop__circle\"><a class=\"c-biz-loop__link\" href=\"business/circular-energy/\"><span>資源循環<br>エネルギー</a></div></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"p-f-dev\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"p-f-dev__inner\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-dev__head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"p-f-section-head__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-en\">Development</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-jp\">開発案件</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"p-f-dev__body p-f-dev__body--saf\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-dev__list\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-dev__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"p-f-dev__link\" href=\"business/circular-energy/saf/\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"p-f-dev__image\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/assets/img/front/dev_saf.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-f-dev__text\">持続可能な航空燃料(SAF)等の安定的・効率的な生産技術開発事業</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"p-f-corp\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"p-f-corp__wrapper\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-corp__inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-corp__head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"p-f-section-head__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-en\">Corporate</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-jp\">企業情報</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head__more\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"p-f-section-head__link\" href=\"/corporate/\">詳しく見る</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-corp__image\"></div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"p-f-corp__body\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-corp__body-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t当社は1965年に運送業「平野産業」として創業。建設工事、産業廃棄物の処理、リサイクルと事業を拡大し、2011年からは廃棄物を燃料にした発電事業を行ってきました。<br>\r\n\t\t\t\t世界的に大きな環境問題が山積する中、資源循環、再生可能エネルギー開発事業の戦略的投資を加速させ、生産性と付加価値の向上、収益基盤の強化に挑戦。世の中の期待を超える社会的価値をつくり上げ、秋田の未来の創造に努めます。\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\t<div class=\"p-f-news\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"p-f-news__inner\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-news__head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"p-f-section-head__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-en\">IR</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-f-section-head__title-jp\">IR情報</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-section-head__more\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"p-f-section-head__link\" href=\"ir/\">IRニュース一覧</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"p-f-news__body\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"c-newslist js-motion\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"c-newslist__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"c-newslist__link\" href=\"https://www.united-k.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/r5Jisseki.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__title\">令和５年度　処理実績</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"c-newslist__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"c-newslist__link\" href=\"https://www.united-k.jp/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Financial_Statements_Notice_FY43.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-newslist__title\">第43期（令和６年度）貸借対照表・損益計算書</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\